Jennifer Lopez, 53, has appeared in a lovely display of snaps alongside husband Ben Affleck as the star celebrates her 53rd birthday. The two could be seen out on a barge as the singer cosied up to her husband.  The star was dressed in a white floral dress as she relaxed alongside Ben.  She also wore dark shaded alongside a silver bracelet as she wore her luscious brown hair long.  Meanwhile, Ben was dressed in a smooth blue shirt, white undershirt and blue dress pants.  He completed his look with white trainers.